## Overview

This repository contains our reliable file transfer project over UDP.  
Phase 2 focuses on **RDT 2.2 with bit errors**, and Phase 3 extends the work toward **RDT 3.0 with packet loss and retransmission**.

The project uses stop-and-wait behavior, alternating sequence numbers, checksums for corruption detection, acknowledgments, timeout-based retransmission, and binary file transfer using a BMP test file.

